title: The Bat Segundo Show -- Torrent Pack #7
description:
This is the seventh torrent pack of the literary podcast, The Bat Segundo Show, 
which can be found at http://www.edrants.com/segundo.

The podcast features indepth interviews with contemporary authors and is 
hosted by the alcoholic and blacklisted DJ, Bat Segundo.

This pack includes Shows #121-140.

121. Gary Shteyngart
122. Richard Flanagan
123. Steven Hall
124. Alternative Press Expo, Part One
125. Alternative Press Expo, Part Two
126. Alternative Press Expo, Part Three
127. Michelle Richmond
128. Katherine Taylor & Mindy Schneider
129. Katie Roiphe
130. Katharine Weber & Levi Asher
131. Kate Christenen
132. Matthew Sharpe & Megan Sullivan
133. William Gibson
134. Marianne Wiggins
135. Gabe Kaplan
136. Antoine Wilson

Thanks for listening!
